{
  "page": "Feature quote/176",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“It was different when there was a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">Stark</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>. But the <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">old wolf</a>'s dead and <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">young one</a>'s gone south to play the <b>game of thrones</b>.” —<a href=\"/index.php/The_Liddle\" title=\"The Liddle\">Liddle</a><br />“The wolves will come again.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen Reed</a><br />“And how would you be knowing, boy?” —Liddle<br />“I dreamed it.” —Jojen Reed.<br />“Some nights I dream of me mother that I buried nine years past, but when I wake, she's not back to us.” —Liddle<br />“There are dreams and dreams, my lord.” —Jojen Reed<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_24\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 24\">Chapter 24</a>, Bran II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403102755\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 124/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 300/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip